      "name": "Pensée systémique",
      "abstract": "Systèmes thinking helps creators et technologists understand why local interventions can produce indirect, delayed ou counterintuitive effects.",
      "description": "Systèmes thinking est un approach that studies elements through their relationships, feedback, boundaries, delays, stocks, flows et patterns de behavior over time.",
